We usually have one for everyone who has signed up.. So I will start this years.
Just copy and paste message and add your details.

As usual, I will be organising a convoy from the north down to the meeting point. Anyone else from the north is more than welcome to join up with us.
And maybe this year we will try and get to all the meeting points on time.
So add forum name, bus details and your names.
